snippet.title: Fishing Star World Tour - OFFICIAL TRAILER [Switch]
snippet.description:
Get hooked on fishy fun for the whole family in this immersive and authentic angling experience! Fishing Star World Tour offers a variety of play styles to suit any fisherman’s preferences, and is sure to offer an ocean of entertainment.

For more information, please visit www.aksysgames.com/fishingstar

Key Features:

Other Fish In The Sea - Fishing Star World Tour includes over 180 kinds of fish. Keep track of the different species you’ve found in the “Fish Book”! Will you find every fish?

International Waters -  Cast your line in over 40 different scenic locations from around the world.

Whatever Floats Your Boat - Maximize your gameplay experience with custom gear, including over 70 different kinds of fishing rods!

A Trollicking Good Time - Grab your Nintendo Labo™ Toy-Con Fishing Rod for an exciting trolling mini-game! Catch the biggest fish you can from your speeding vessel!
